Beyond the Clouds;;1995;;Not Rated;;Drama,Romance;;6.5;;Michelangelo Antonioni,Wim Wenders;;Fanny Ardant,Chiara Caselli,Irène Jacob,John Malkovich,Sophie Marceau,Vincent Perez,Jean Reno,Kim Rossi Stuart,Inés Sastre,Peter Weller,Marcello Mastroianni,Jeanne Moreau,Enrica Antonioni,Carine Angeli,Alessandra Bonarota,Laurence Calabrese,Tracey Caligiuri,Hervé Décalion;;Four short tales are linked by a story filmed by Wim Wenders. Taking place in Ferrara, Portofino, Aix en Provence, and Paris, each story, always with a woman as its crux, invites the viewer to an inner travel, as Antonioni says "towards the true image of that absolute and mysterious reality that nobody will ever see".;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0114086/